Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.80,0:26:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那"東西"是那副模樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.20,0:26:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
